data.description: WOW! Quality-built home by award-winning Sasser Construction! Located in highly sought-after Parkside at Bennett’s Creek area in Waterfront at Parkside community. You don’t want to miss this captivating and move-in ready home! The kitchen, dining room, and living room all open up to one another and boast a bright & airy floor plan perfect for entertaining or enjoying family time. Located on the 1st floor you'll find the master bedroom, a private office/study, beautiful stone gas fireplace, and laundry room. The 2nd floor includes 3 additional bedrooms, a loft/living room area, and full bathroom. Enjoy the convenience of a dual-zone heating and a/c system. The beautifully maintained yard includes a sprinkler system and fenced backyard. Enjoy the beautiful covered back porch. The 2-car garage has rear driveway access. Park includes Playground, frisbee golf, skateboard ramp, picnic areas & hiking trails. Located close to highways, military bases and shopping.
